    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>“不能逃避，去驾驶你的机甲。”</p><span id="more"></span><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xgyxss/picgo@main/img/hexo/%E3%80%8A%E4%BD%A0%E6%83%B3%E6%B4%BB%E5%87%BA%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E5%89%A7%E7%85%A701.webp" alt="《你想活出怎样的人生》剧照01"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xgyxss/picgo@main/img/hexo/%E3%80%8A%E4%BD%A0%E6%83%B3%E6%B4%BB%E5%87%BA%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E5%89%A7%E7%85%A702.webp" alt="《你想活出怎样的人生》剧照02"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xgyxss/picgo@main/img/hexo/%E3%80%8A%E4%BD%A0%E6%83%B3%E6%B4%BB%E5%87%BA%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E5%89%A7%E7%85%A703.webp" alt="《你想活出怎样的人生》剧照03"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xgyxss/picgo@main/img/hexo/%E3%80%8A%E4%BD%A0%E6%83%B3%E6%B4%BB%E5%87%BA%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E5%89%A7%E7%85%A704.webp" alt="《你想活出怎样的人生》剧照04"></p><p>“不能逃避，去驾驭你的人生。”</p><blockquote><p>Stay Hungry, Stay Foolish.</p></blockquote><p><u><em><strong>谋定而后动</strong></em></u>，想做就去做，任何时候开始都不算晚，犯错总比不做好。</p><p>有些事情现在不尝试，也许这辈子都不会再有勇气去做了。</p><p>大胆去尝试，即刻。</p><p>YOLO！！</p>]]></content>
    
    
